  author    = "Georges, Vanessa and Courtemanche, Fran{\c c}ois and Senecal,
               Sylvain and Baccino, Thierry and Fredette, Marc and Leger,
               Pierre-Majorique",
  abstract  = "In this paper, we present an off-the-shelf UX evaluation tool
